data.description: Beautiful Tropical Oasis. Looking to be on a permanent vacation, look no further. This home features Brazilian upgraded counter tops in the kitchen and baths with travertine backsplash featuring Bristol York cabinetry with soft close doors and drawers. The kitchen cabinets also have remote control under counter lighting and crown molding. The Master bath boasts Travertine walk in shower w/antique brass fixtures. The landscaping gives the feel of being on a tropical island featuring a beautiful screened in Tiki with 2 live edge bars and a whiskey barrel table along with beautiful floors that have a custom beach sand appearance. The yard has been upgraded with irrigation, tropical trees and shrubbery along with 4 banana trees.  Many of the Christmas palms have solar up lighting for that Tropical ambiance. Plenty of storage w/3 included outbuildings. The 12'x15' pool is a perfect place to cool off and enjoy your Oasis. You will also enjoy the new, 6 person Hot Tub w/beautiful step, style entrance deck. The entire back yard is fenced and the screened garage has a mini split AC for a perfect work space or mancave. You must see this home in person to see all its upgrades and features.
